# Legal pages

Stayvo legal copy: `app/terms/page.tsx`, `app/privacy/page.tsx`, support email in `lib/support-email.ts`.

When changing **pricing, Stripe/billing, subscription tiers, data collection, subprocessors, account deletion, or support contact**:

1. Read `docs/legal-pages-checklist.md` and update the affected legal section(s).
2. Bump `LAST_UPDATED` on each edited legal page.
3. Mention legal updates in the PR/commit summary.

Do not change legal text for purely cosmetic UI unless user-facing promises change (e.g. FAQ on cancellation).
